Some armed bandits have invaded a villlage in Ebonyi state and wiped out many innocent souls. According to information by one Amaka Ekwo on social media platform, twitter, the armed bandits stormed Ngbo in Ohaukwu local government area of Ebonyi State, yesterday the 10th of March, 2020 killing about 15 persons and burning down their homes and properties. In a video making the rounds online, the dead bodies of the victims were captured as villagers shed uncontrollable tears. Watch video below: Source